{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ffa2d023b4","title":"给马寅初的一封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1ebeb44121","index":0,"year":1951,"month":11,"day":15,"articleId":"ffa2d023b4"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"98201c8e7d","type":"title","text":"给马黄初的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"},{"id":"e0ae848939","type":"paragraph","text":"寅初：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"},{"id":"f43f9c29c0","type":"paragraph","text":"关于学生健康问题前与先生谈过。此问题深值注意，提议采取行政步骤，具体地解决此问题，提出“健康第一，学习第二”的方针。我认为（中共华东局一月十一日电报一件附上，请查阅，其中第三项谈此问题）是正确的，请马副部长同志商韵处理为盼","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"},{"id":"1c9b8c69f7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"},{"id":"a5d0157bf7","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年十一月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"},{"id":"c6793fc938","type":"paragraph","text":"附：中共华东局一月十一日电报","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"},{"id":"a897d6880b","type":"subtitle","text":"“健康第一，学习第二","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"},{"id":"d51ad54b9f","type":"paragraph","text":"节录中共华东局一月十一日向中央报告","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"},{"id":"a6ceea00d8","type":"paragraph","text":"关于学校工作的指示电文","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"},{"id":"137671f47a","type":"subtitle","text":"“（三）转入正常学习，又须防止过去加多课程硬赶功课的","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"},{"id":"bcb41f47a3","type":"paragraph","text":"偏向。从此次参加军校学生之体格检查中，即可看出，由于国民觉长期反动统治的结果，学生体质虚弱，患病者很多。但解放以来，各地也未能很好注意“健康第一，学习第二之原则，因此造成公立学校之体格最差，大学较中学又差的现象还严重存在，这点应引起十分警惕。应按华东局高教会议的规定，适当减少正课时间，照顾学生健康需要。…","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"},{"id":"46460086af","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席批语：这是正确的。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4"}],"page":{"id":"58950baad8","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ffa2d023b4","start":66,"end":67}}}},"__N_SSG":true}